### Inject Custom Code
For third-party scripts (analytics, chat widgets, etc.) that don't have a native Rocket integration:
- Project Settings → Inject Custom Code
- Paste script tags — Rocket adds them to the correct location in `layout.tsx`
- Supports: `<head>` scripts, `<body>` scripts, meta tags
